title: S12 Ep41: Have You Been Hexed?: Recognizing and Breaking Curses
itunes:title: Have You Been Hexed?: Recognizing and Breaking Curses
description:
Beyond The Darkness welcomes Dr Alexandra Chauran as we ask, Is everything in your life going wrong? Is it a curse or just plain bad luck? Today we explore whether or not you've been hexed and breaking curses of all kinds, even those we've placed on ourselves.

Dr, Alexandra Chauran: http://www.seepsychic.com/
